<p>

<li><I>Ibid</I>., pg. 81.

<p>

<li>&quot;The American Family Time Satisfaction Study.&quot;  Massachusetts
Mutual Life Insurance Company and <I>Family Fun</I> Magazine,
Nov. 1993: pg. 5.

<p>

<li><I>Ibid</I>., pg. 39.

<p>

<li><I>Ibid</I>., pg. 5 of graphs and charts.

