<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/heritage/p_review/spring95/jarvth.html 204.71.237.79 19970210141455 text/html 25243
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 14:15:37 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:29:27 GMT
